5. Product boundaries

Do not move these into Theia ownership:
- module identity for GodCode, KaiPrompt, Neural-Space-Pro, and other tool pockets
- local runtime behavior in server.js
- existing tool routing logic

Theia should augment:
- workspace file access
- terminals and background processes
- coding assistants and extension workflows
- launcher unification

6. Acceptance criteria

SkaixuProIDEia is done when:
- the base SkaixuPro-IDE platform remains intact.
- the upgraded build launches as a full app.
- users can move from launcher to coding environment to tool module without preview widgets.
- Theia provides support functions but not product identity.

